qas.question: How many ducks did China produce for consumption in 2011?

answers.text: China producing two thirds of the total, some 1.7 billion birds

qas.question: What other countries are important to the duck husbandry business?

answers.text: Vietnam, Thailand, Malaysia, Myanmar, Indonesia and South Korea (12% in total)

answers.text: France (3.5%) is the largest producer in the West,
